## Task Management

How to track progress and stay organized.

### 1. Plan First
Write plan to tasks/todo.md with checkable items before starting.

### 2. Track Progress
Mark items complete as you go. Don't batch updates.

### 3. Verify Before Done
- Tests pass (or justified why not needed)
- No breaking changes
- Code follows project conventions
- Changes only touch what's necessary

### 4. Document Results
Add review section to tasks/todo.md after completing.

### 5. Capture Lessons
Update memory/lessons.md after corrections or discoveries.

